    "excerpt": "The Opening Prayer given in the U.S. Senate on 17 May 1988. . . .",
    "content": "<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">\nGuest Chaplain: Rabbi Richard Marcovitz, Congregation Bnai Israel, Pittsburgh<br />\nDate of Prayer: 17 May 1988<br />\nSponsor:\n</div>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"/contributing/upload/\">Contribute&nbsp;a&nbsp;translation</a></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Source (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nIn but a few days,<br />\nthe world Jewish community<br />\nwill observe the festival of Pentecost—<br />\nthe anniversary of the giving of the Law on Mount Sinai.<br />\nThat sublime law<br />\nas exemplified by the Ten Commandments<br />\nhas endured through the ages,<br />\nlifting the hearts and minds of humanity.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nWe pray, O Lord,<br />\nthat Your presence<br />\nwill inspire these creators of law<br />\nin their tasks;<br />\nthat they may aspire to the extraordinary,<br />\nmaking the law of the land<br />\nto guide and to protect,<br />\nto free and to instruct.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nMay Your Kingship of peace<br />\nbe established<br />\nwith great speed<br />\nso that all who are fettered or oppressed<br />\nwill know blessing.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nMay the work of the minds, hearts, and hands<br />\nof those who make up this singular body<br />\nbe established<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Psalms 90:17.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nworking in partnership with You, O Lord,<br />\nto bring about a world filled with blessing.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nAnd we respond, &#8220;<em>Amen</em>.&#8221;\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<p>100th Congress, 2nd Session. <a href=\"https://www.c-span.org/video/?c4508012/user-clip-rabbi-richard-marcovitz-congregation-bnai-israel-pittsburgh-pa\">C-SPAN</a>.<br />\n<em>Congressional Record</em>, <a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/100/crecb/1988/05/17/GPO-CRECB-1988-pt8-5-1.pdf\">Vol. 134, Part 8 — Bound Edition, p. 11192</a>.</p>\n<p><iframe width=530 height=312 src='https://www.c-span.org/video/standalone/?c4508012/user-clip-rabbi-richard-marcovitz-congregation-bnai-israel-pittsburgh-pa' allowfullscreen='allowfullscreen' frameborder=0></iframe><span class=\"\" style=\"display:block;clear:both;height: 0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;\"></span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_47619\" style=\"width: 225px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Congressional-Record-v.-134-part-8-17-May-1988.-p.-11192.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47619\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Congressional-Record-v.-134-part-8-17-May-1988.-p.-11192-215x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"215\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-47619\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Congressional-Record-v.-134-part-8-17-May-1988.-p.-11192-215x300.png 215w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Congressional-Record-v.-134-part-8-17-May-1988.-p.-11192-733x1024.png 733w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Congressional-Record-v.-134-part-8-17-May-1988.-p.-11192.png 1170w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 215px) 100vw, 215px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-47619\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Congressional Record v. 134, part 8 &#8211; 17 May 1988. p. 11192</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">Notes</span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" style=\"display: none;; display: none;\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\"></span></p></div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container__1\" style=\"\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">Notes</caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >1</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Cf. Psalms 90:17.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody> </table> </div></div><script type=\"text/javascript\"> function footnote_expand_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').show(); jQuery('#footnote_reference_container_collapse_button__1').text('−'); } function footnote_collapse_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').hide(); jQuery('#footnote_reference_container_collapse_button__1').text('+'); } function footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1() { if (jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').is(':hidden')) { footnote_expand_reference_container__1(); } else { footnote_collapse_reference_container__1(); } } function footnote_moveToReference__1(p_str_TargetID) { footnote_expand_reference_container__1(); var l_obj_Target = jQuery('#' + p_str_TargetID); if (l_obj_Target.length) { jQuery( 'html, body' ).delay( 0 ); jQuery('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: l_obj_Target.offset().top - window.innerHeight * 0.2 }, 380); } } function footnote_moveToAnchor__1(p_str_TargetID) { footnote_expand_reference_container__1(); var l_obj_Target = jQuery('#' + p_str_TargetID); if (l_obj_Target.length) { jQuery( 'html, body' ).delay( 0 ); jQuery('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: l_obj_Target.offset().top - window.innerHeight * 0.2 }, 380); } }</script>",
